<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Automatic OT Check-out Recorded</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0f2f5;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f0f2f5;padding:40px 16px;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);">
        <tr><td style="background:#0f172a;padding:20px 32px;">
          <span style="color:#fff;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.3px;">Sky<span style="color:#38bdf8;">Time</span>Hub</span>
        </td></tr>
        <tr><td style="background:#6366f1;height:4px;padding:0;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding:36px 32px 32px;">
          <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
            <tr><td style="background:#eef2ff;border-radius:100px;padding:5px 14px;">
              <span style="color:#6366f1;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.3px;">🤖 SYSTEM AUTO CHECK-OUT</span>
            </td></tr>
          </table>
          <h1 style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;">Automatic OT Check-out Recorded</h1>
          <p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#64748b;font-size:14px;">The system has automatically checked you out as your OT session exceeded the allowed window.</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#374151;font-size:15px;">Xin chào <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong>,</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#374151;font-size:15px;">You did not manually check out within 2 hours after your planned OT ended. The system has automatically recorded your check-out time as the planned end time for OT plan <strong>{{planTitle}}</strong>.</p>
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:28px;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;font-weight:500;width:40%;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">OT Plan</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">{{planTitle}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;font-weight:500;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Check-in Time</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">{{checkInAt}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;font-weight:500;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Auto Check-out Time</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">{{checkOutAt}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;background:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;font-weight:500;">Actual Duration</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;">{{actualDuration}}</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
            <tr><td style="background:#eef2ff;border-left:4px solid #6366f1;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:14px 16px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#374151;">Your department leader will review and confirm your actual OT hours. If you have any concerns, please contact your leader directly.</p>
            </td></tr>
          </table>
          <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
            <tr><td style="border-radius:8px;background:#6366f1;">
              <a href="{{otAssignmentUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:13px 28px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;">View Details →</a>
            </td></tr>
          </table>
        </td></tr>
        <tr><td style="background:#f8fafc;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:20px 32px;text-align:center;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 4px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;">© 2026 SkyTimeHub. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;">Email này được gửi tự động, vui lòng không trả lời.</p>
        </td></tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
